principles of men, always in your mind. There
are three philosophies every man should take
note of. Lemme break them. Every man should:
1. Think faster. Dont think fast, even women can
do that. Think faster.

swore never to leave me for the rest of my life if

A Farmer caught a thief who had been stealing his yams and decided to drag him to the village square. Half-way to the square, the thief said to the man: ''pleade I av forgotten my slipperd in the farm, can I go and get them?
The former obliged, ''Hurry up! I wud be waiting for u here.''
He waited endlessly and realised he had been fooled. He went home and told his elder brother wat happened. His brother brutally slapped him and said, ''You are extremely dumb! U shud have told the thief to wait while u go get his slippers for him..''
